project:
Left Click to pull the trigger of your weapon
|Left Click to release trigger
|Landing on Green in Attack Mode will fire the weapon
|Landing on Gray in Attack Mode will jam the weapon
|Landing on Green in Defend Mode will dodge incoming fire
|Landing on Red in Defend Mode will damage the weapon
|Avoid taking weapon damage, as it is permanent
|After defeating an enemy, select on upgrade to a component on the weapon
|Can you defeat all 6 enemy weapons?
